{"tid":1681981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒 眾籌 同埋國際 twitter戰線 冇人講？","createTime":"2019-10-29T19:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T14:13:26.000Z","uid":249945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b7df1332d7cd4e5450fa78a1ef3acb67283b5227","tid":1681981,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T19:00:50.000Z","msg":"【🇺🇸 DQ事件｜參議員促盡快通過《香港人權民主法案》】<br />\n<br />\nDQ事件引起參議院關注，外交關係委員會主席Jim Risch、委員會首席民主黨參議員Bob Menendez、共和黨參議員Tom Cotton、Josh Hawley等相繼出聲，促請參議院盡快通過《香港人權民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n會見過黃之鋒的Josh Hawley直言，DQ事件反映香港的選舉根本不是公平公開，參議院有更多理由，立即通過法案。<br />\n<br />\nJim Risch則指出，DQ事件是中共再度干預香港事務的明證；Tom Cotton表示，若然香港希望維持有別於大陸的「兩制」，必須停止引入這類中共暴政式政治審查，並促認為參院加快審議法案。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以去感謝對方，希望法案盡快通過👇🏻<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenTomCotton/status/1189160656756453376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenTomCotton%2Fstatus%2F1189160656756453376&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=8e85aadd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenTomCotton%2Fstatus%2F1189160656756453376&h=36e6c0f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenTomCotton/status/1189160656756453376</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1189146016571908096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1189146016571908096&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=1d0b54fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1189146016571908096&h=4fbb5f06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1189146016571908096</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenateForeign/status/1189238177577521152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenateForeign%2Fstatus%2F1189238177577521152&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=54229cd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenateForeign%2Fstatus%2F1189238177577521152&h=73fa4e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenateForeign/status/1189238177577521152</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorMenendez/status/1189227028056281089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorMenendez%2Fstatus%2F1189227028056281089&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=26cb1b72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorMenendez%2Fstatus%2F1189227028056281089&h=8b0aeffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenatorMenendez/status/1189227028056281089</a><br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n🗺【支持眾志國際連結眾籌】<br />\n讓香港人權民主法案遍地開花｜<a href=\"http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fintlcrowdfunding&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=f88304c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding</a><br />\n<br />\n『零時差』收取國際資訊 <br />\n👉 <a href=\"http://t.me/demosisto_Int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdemosisto_Int&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=fc9fcfdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/demosisto_Int</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fintlcrowdfunding&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=f88304c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding</a>"},{"pid":"7827de8abf3eb65d055516e009ebc97bc9deac91","tid":1681981,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T19:01:31.000Z","msg":"push ar"},{"pid":"733bad78ed15c88e01ed65267c9b1494ab24cf5b","tid":1681981,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T19:02:19.000Z","msg":"g phone為我哋入獄冇發生過？"},{"pid":"96ab04864fdea91801a1d1ad6809fbc9b85a3722","tid":168198